@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 190

actor "Nhan vien" as Staff
participant "StaffFeaturePanels.billingPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "StaffFeatureController\n(Facade)" as Facade
participant "BillingController" as Controller
participant "StaffService" as Service
participant "StaffBillingRepository" as Repository
participant "JpaStaffDataStore" as DataStore
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Staff, DB: QUY TRINH TINH TOAN HOA DON DONG LOAT HANG THANG

Staff -> View : 1. Chon thang + bam 'Tinh hoa don'
View -> Facade : 2. generateInvoices(month, electricRate, waterRate, garbageFee)
activate Facade

Facade -> Controller : 3. generateInvoices(month,...)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 4. generateInvoices(YearMonth,...)
activate Service
Service -> Repository : 5. generateInvoices(period,...)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataStore : 6. generateInvoices(period,...)
activate DataStore

DataStore -> DB : 7. processAutoBilling(period) va insert HOA_DON
activate DB
DB -->> DataStore : 8. Danh sach hoa don moi
DataStore -->> Repository : 9. So hoa don da tao
Repository -->> Service : 10. So hoa don da tao
Service -->> Controller : 11. So hoa don da tao
Controller -->> Facade : 12. So hoa don da tao
Facade -->> View : 13. Hien thi ket qua tao hoa don

deactivate DB
deactivate DataStore
deactivate Repository
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
deactivate Facade

View -> View : 14. Refresh bang invoices()
View -->> Staff : 15. Hien danh sach hoa don vua tao
@enduml
